  "method": [
    "In a pot, heat olive oil, garlic cloves, and jalapeño pepper on low heat.",
    "Then add chili powder, beans, 1/2 cup of stock, cumin, and cook for",
    "25-35 minutes. In the end, add bell pepper and salt.",
    "Add garlic cloves in the remaining olive oil",
    "and heat them. Pour the remaining stock, bring it to boil. Add rice,",
    "reduce the heat, and cook for almost 15-20 minutes.",
    "When rice is cooked, add spices.",
    "Arrange black beans and rice on a serving platter."
  ],
